org.sql: SELECT journals.* FROM journals WHERE journals.journable_id = "$1" AND journals.journable_type = "$2" AND version > 1 ORDER BY journals.version ASC, journals.created_at ASC

rewrites.sql: SELECT journals.* FROM journals WHERE journals.journable_id = "$1" AND journals.journable_type = "$2" AND version > 1 ORDER BY journals.version ASC, journals.created_at ASC LIMIT 1
